{"tid":2008226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰﹕五區公投承諾已不存在","createTime":"2020-05-09T01:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T15:17:22.000Z","uid":297241,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca9cc9897dfd6f3bee873967e4ae25c2addb63d","tid":2008226,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰﹕五區公投承諾已不存在<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】「熱普城」選舉聯盟主打「五區公投 全民制憲 永續基本法」，最終只得熱血公民鄭松泰勝出，鄭承認成績未如人意，更明言主張的政治綱領失敗，<span style=\"color: red;\">「我最大的選舉承諾(五區公投)已經不存在」。他形容自己在立法會彈性相對高，可四周協調「擔任說客的角色」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰接受本報訪問時說，將在議會內協助和為抗爭者「在輿論上開路」，但<span style=\"color: red;\">表明自己未來「無法走去(抗爭)戰線的最前方」</span>，因一露面已惹來警員關注。對於主張勇武抗爭的熱血公民被外界批評「得把口」，鄭說：「得把口講，好過『篤灰』和割席。」"},{"pid":"dba2d018555ae62b9777f0c08e4133502535eab8","tid":2008226,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64f4c3ad77dd0ad80a22db32802c260549bec48","tid":2008226,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係玩完<br />\n<br />\n勇武<br />\n和理非<br />\n<br />\n都完全唔認同佢<br />\n<br />\n琴日個表現  差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43f855f477badf2668b7c7eab93b87884ab63da","tid":2008226,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEWCJJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEWCJJk.jpg&h=af5d00e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FChFGu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFChFGu1.jpg&h=7314f500&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d496e6dee1238e82a83b0bdc012d7a3ff6098ade","tid":2008226,"uid":6063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"你睇下胡志偉點食崔淚彈"},{"pid":"e37389d4d425d9de77c4084627f17885f95721d